reg_info.citation: O. Reg. 418/01: DELEGATION OF AUTHORITY - PARRY SOUND AREA PLANNING BOARD
reg_info.act_under: Planning Act   Loi sur l’aménagement du territoire

content.content: 1. The Minister’s authority under section 51 of the Act to approve a plan of subdivision is delegated to the Parry Sound Area Planning Board with respect to applications whose file numbers are set out in the Schedule. O. Reg. 418/01, s. 1.
